# Real-Time COVID-19 Dashboard

An interactive dashboard that visualizes global COVID-19 trends using live data from public APIs. Built with Streamlit and Plotly for clean, responsive visualizations.

## Features
- Live COVID-19 data via external API
- Country-specific case tracking
- Daily vs cumulative graphs
- Responsive charts using Plotly
- Easy deployment on Streamlit Cloud

## Technologies Used
- Python
- Streamlit
- Pandas
- Plotly
- REST API (disease.sh)

